# DTSE Implementation

When implementing DTSE improvements, follow this rule.

## Commands

| Command | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `npm run test` | Unit tests (Vitest) |
| `npm run build` | Build + TypeScript check |
| `npm run test:e2e` | E2E (Cypress; starts server on 4173) |
| `npm run dev` | Dev server (port 3000) |

## Key paths

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/components/DTSE/` | DTSE stage components (DTSEDashboard, DTSEContextStage, etc.) |
| `src/utils/dtseLiveSignatures.ts` | Live failure signatures; price compression clamp at line 56 |
| `src/data/dtseContent.ts` | Protocol briefs, PROTOCOL_BRIEF_OVERRIDES, deriveDefaultProtocolBrief |

## Plan and rules

- **Plan:** `docs/DTSE_IMPROVEMENT_PLAN.md` — phases, checklist, proof, live check
- **UI rules:** `docs/DTSE_DASHBOARD_UI_UX_RULES_V1.md`
- **Audit:** `docs/DTSE_NOISE_VS_SIGNAL_AUDIT.md`

## Before claiming done

1. Run `npm run test`, `npm run build`, `npm run test:e2e` — all must pass.
2. Use **verification-before-completion** or **depin-verification-before-completion** skill.
3. Before PR: use Source Control → Agent Review to compare against main.
